==English==
===Verb===
'''[[make]] one's [[skin]] [[crawl]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[disturb]] or [[bother]]; to [[frighten]] or [[disgust]].
#:''The sound of fingernails on a chalkboard just '''makes my skin crawl'''.''
